<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Document</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Open+Sans:wght@400;600;700&display=swap"
 
    />
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: "Open Sans", sans-serif;
        background-color: #e7f0ea;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .textColor {
        color: #052311;
      }
      .primaryColor {
        color: #0e6431;
      }
      .headline {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: 600;
      }
      .titleSize {
        font-size: 1rem;
        font-weight: 400;
        color: #052311;
      }
      .textSize {
        font-size: 0.975rem;
        color: #052311;
      }
      .importantText {
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #0e6431;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  
  <body>
    <h1 class="headline" >
      Dear Hiring Team,
    </h1>

    <p class="textSize" style="padding-top: 20px; padding-bottom: 20px">
      A new job seeker has expressed interested in finding a job through our plateform.
    </p>
   <ul>

    <li>
      <p>User's email: <span class="importantText"><%=email%></span></p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p>Skill: <span class="importantText"><%=skill%></span></p>
    </li>
   </ul>
    <p class="textSize">We recommended following up to provide them with relevant job oppotunities.</p>
    <div style="margin-top: 20px;">
      <p class="textSize">Best regards</p>
      <p class="textSize" style="padding-bottom: 10px">Your Automated System</p>
    </div>
  
  </body>
</html>
